slightly /ˈslaɪtlɪ/

1. ADV Slightly means to some degree but not to a very large degree. 轻微地; 稍微 

例： His family then moved to a slightly larger house. 他的家后来搬到了一间稍微大一点儿的房子。 

例： Each person learns in a slightly different way. 每个人学习的方式都略有不同。

